</span> 标题：门楣（lintel）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מַשְׁקוֹף</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mashqof)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:7\">EXO 12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:22\">EXO 12:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:23\">EXO 12:23</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>门楣是门框的顶梁（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2 门、门口 (door, doorway)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2&gt;</a> ）。参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.4 门柱 (doorpost)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.4&gt;</a> 中的插图。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.4 门柱 (doorpost)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.4&gt;</a> 中的讨论。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
